.TH CONSTANTS 5NEMO "8 July 2022"

.SH NAME
constants \- list of useful constants

.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Here we tabulate some convenience values we often use in astronomy.
Only a few are available in programs that use \fInemoinp(1NEMO)\fP

.SH "CONSTANTS"
.nf
.ta +1.5i 
